[标准周期]
\end_layout

\end_inset

以 
\begin_inset Formula $2\mathrm{\pi}$
\end_inset

 为周期且在 
\begin_inset Formula $(0,2\mathrm{\pi})$
\end_inset

 上平方可积的函数都可以作 Fourier 级数展开：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(\theta)\equiv\ip{\theta}{u}\doteq\sum_{n\in\mathbb{Z}}\underbrace{\frac{\exp(\ii n\theta)}{\sqrt{2\mathrm{\pi}}}}_{\ip{x}{n}}\underbrace{\int_{0}^{2\mathrm{\pi}}\frac{\exp(-\ii n\theta')}{\sqrt{2\mathrm{\pi}}}u(\theta')\dd{\theta'}}_{u_{n}\equiv\ip{n}{u}}
\]

\end_inset

