\begin_layout Proof
将 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{Co}}$
\end_inset

 代入三维 Fourier 变换的定义，会遇到积分不收敛的问题。注意到 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{Co}}(r)=\lim_{\alpha\to0}V_{\mathrm{Yu}}(r)$
\end_inset

，可以先求出 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{Yu}}$
\end_inset

 的 Fourier 变换，再对所得结果取极限，从而得到 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{Co}}$
\end_inset

 的 Fourier 变换：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tilde{V}_{\mathrm{C}}(\vec{k})=\lim_{\alpha\to0}\tilde{V}_{\alpha}(\vec{k})=\lim_{\alpha\to0}\iiint_{\mathbb{R}^{3}(\vec{x})}\frac{\ee^{-\ii\vec{k}\cdot\vec{x}}}{(2\mathrm{\pi})^{3/2}}\frac{\ee^{-\alpha r}}{r}
\]

\end_inset

由于 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{Yu}}(r)$
\end_inset

 关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}^{3}(\vec{x})$
\end_inset

 的原点对称，因此在球坐标中计算最方便：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{x}=(r\sin\theta\cos\phi)\vec{e}_{x}+(r\sin\theta\sin\phi)\vec{e}_{y}+(r\cos\theta)\vec{e}_{z}
\]

\end_inset

原则上，
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{e}_{z}$
\end_inset

 的方向可以任取，最简单的方案是：令其
\color red
平行
\color inherit
于 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{k}$
\end_inset

，即 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{k}=k\vec{e}_{z}$
\end_inset

，于是有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\tilde{V}_{\alpha}(\vec{k}) & =\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd{r}\int_{0}^{\mathrm{\pi}}\dd{\theta}\int_{0}^{2\mathrm{\pi}}\dd{\phi}\frac{\ee^{-\ii kr\cos\theta}}{(2\mathrm{\pi})^{3/2}}\frac{\ee^{-\alpha r}}{r}r^{2}\sin\theta\\
 & =\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\mathrm{\pi}}}\int_{0}^{\infty}\underbrace{\left(\int_{0}^{\mathrm{\pi}}\ee^{-\ii kr\cos\theta}\sin\theta\dd{\theta}\right)}_{u\coloneqq\cos\theta}\ee^{-\alpha r}r\dd{r}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\mathrm{\pi}}}\int_{0}^{\infty}\frac{\ee^{\ii kr}-\ee^{-\ii kr}}{\ii kr}\ee^{-\alpha r}r\dd{r}\\
 & =\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\mathrm{\pi}}}\frac{1}{\ii k}\left(\frac{-1}{-\alpha+\ii k}-\frac{-1}{-\alpha-\ii k}\right)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\mathrm{\pi}}}\frac{2}{\alpha^{2}+k^{2}}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

